data.description: This impeccably maintained 4-bed, 3-bath home, is just a 5-minutes from PGA, Universal Studios, Dallas Tollway, and multiple top-tier schools. The kitchen is a culinary haven with lavish granite countertops, is every chef's dream. Bench seating in the dining area creates a cozy atmosphere, while plantation shutters offer light control and privacy. Cathedral ceilings add grandeur to the living space. Luxuries abound, including a spa shower, a Jack and Jill bathroom, expansive closets with built-in shelving, cathedral ceilings, stairwell walk-in storage, built-in cabinets, a designer wine bar, and a spacious mudroom. Your organized garage adds convenience to daily life. Entertainment options include a media room and a covered patio and the community offers two pools, a fishing pond, trails, and sports fields. This home seamlessly blends elegance and practicality, creating a life of unparalleled comfort and sophistication. Don't miss out on this one! Seller offering $5,000 concession.
